<view class="diagnose-detail-page">
  <view class="dd-hero card">
    <text class="dd-badge">1v1申论诊断</text>
    <text class="dd-title">先找到失分病因，再决定下一步怎么学</text>
    <text class="dd-desc">参考完整诊断报告结构，先看老师会怎么拆解病因、怎么判断关键卡点、最后怎么形成学习路径。看完再进入正式诊断流程。</text>

    <view class="dd-metrics">
      <view class="dd-metric">
        <text class="dd-metric-value">{{overview.dimensions}}</text>
        <text class="dd-metric-label">诊断维度</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dd-metric">
        <text class="dd-metric-value">{{overview.serviceType}}</text>
        <text class="dd-metric-label">诊断形式</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dd-metric">
        <text class="dd-metric-value">{{overview.outputCount}}</text>
        <text class="dd-metric-label">核心输出</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="dd-tag-row">
      <text wx:for="{{quickTags}}" wx:key="*this" class="dd-tag">{{item}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="dd-score card">
    <view class="dd-student-row">
      <view class="dd-avatar">
        <text class="dd-avatar-text">{{student.name[0]}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dd-student-info">
        <text class="dd-student-name">{{student.name}}</text>
        <text class="dd-student-meta">{{student.exam}}</text>
        <text class="dd-student-meta">示例诊断日期：{{student.diagnosisDate}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="dd-score-panel">
      <view class="dd-score-item">
        <text class="dd-score-value dd-score-warn">{{overview.currentScore}}</text>
        <text class="dd-score-label">当前诊断分</text>
      </view>
      <text class="dd-score-arrow">→</text>
      <view class="dd-score-item">
        <text class="dd-score-value dd-score-target">{{overview.targetScore}}</text>
        <text class="dd-score-label">目标分</text>
      </view>
      <view class="dd-score-item">
        <text class="dd-score-gap">+{{overview.scoreGap}}</text>
        <text class="dd-score-label">提分空间</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="dd-summary-grid">
    <view wx:for="{{highlights}}" wx:key="title" class="dd-summary-card card">
      <text class="dd-section-kicker">{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="dd-summary-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="dd-section-title">诊断结果会先帮你找什么病因</text>
    <view wx:for="{{previewPoints}}" wx:key="name" class="dd-point-card dd-point-card-{{item.tier}}">
      <view class="dd-point-head">
        <text class="dd-point-tier dd-point-tier-{{item.tier}}">{{item.tierText}}</text>
        <text class="dd-point-name">{{item.name}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="dd-point-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="dd-section-title">找病因的依据与输出</text>
    <view wx:for="{{basisRows}}" wx:key="label" class="dd-basis-row">
      <text class="dd-basis-label">{{item.label}}</text>
      <text class="dd-basis-value">{{item.value}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="dd-section-title">卡点体系拆解结果</text>
    <text class="dd-section-subtitle">根据解释文档同步补充：当前这套申论体系共拆出 8 个卡点、23 条学习路径、5 类用户阻力、12 套干预动作。</text>
    <view class="dd-fact-grid">
      <view wx:for="{{systemFacts}}" wx:key="label" class="dd-fact-card">
        <text class="dd-fact-value">{{item.value}}</text>
        <text class="dd-fact-label">{{item.label}}</text>
        <text class="dd-fact-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="dd-section-title">学习规划 · 阶段闯关路径</text>
    <view wx:for="{{phases}}" wx:key="tag" class="dd-phase-card">
      <view class="dd-phase-head">
        <text class="dd-phase-tag">{{item.tag}}</text>
        <text class="dd-phase-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="dd-phase-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <text class="dd-section-title">适合先来做诊断的人</text>
    <view wx:for="{{suitableList}}" wx:key="*this" class="dd-fit-row">
      <text class="dd-fit-dot"></text>
      <text class="dd-fit-text">{{item}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="dd-footer card">
    <text class="dd-footer-title">先看清失分病因，再进入正式诊断流程</text>
    <text class="dd-footer-desc">点下面这个按钮，才会进入你现在已有的“诊断流程”页面。</text>
    <view class="dd-footer-note-list">
      <text class="dd-footer-note">当前页是诊断样例预览，不是正式诊断流程。</text>
      <text class="dd-footer-note">正式购买后，通常会先提交信息，再由老师联系、拆解病因并输出书面诊断报告。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="dd-footer-btn" bindtap="goStartDiagnose">
      <text class="dd-footer-btn-text">去诊断</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

<diagnose-coupon-fab auto-popup="{{true}}"></diagnose-coupon-fab>
